{"id":762974,"date":[{"year":1988,"month":1,"day":1}],"page":"4","source":"本报","region":"","masthead":"画刊","special_issue":"","column":"","genre":"","count":"271","ytitle":"","mtitle":"以文汇友","ftitle":"","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九三八年一月，文汇报在上海诞生。半个世纪来，文汇报几经磨难，几经奋起，现已成为在国内外享有盛誉的报纸。在欢庆本报创刊五十周年之际，深得党和国家领导人以及各界知名人士的关怀和厚爱，或题词撰文，或绘画作诗，以示祝贺。本报今天选登其中的部分作品，以飨读者，并致谢意。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——编者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入8号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1988\\01\\8811040201.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>关山月</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>①报春图　关山月</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入8号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1988\\01\\8811040202.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>周思聪</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>②笛声　周思聪</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入8号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1988\\01\\8811040203.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>刘海粟</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>③齐放　刘海粟</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入8号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1988\\01\\8811040204.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>程十发</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>④芝寿　程十发</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入8号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1988\\01\\8811040205.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>朱屺瞻</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>⑤果甜粽香　朱屺瞻</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入8号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1988\\01\\8811040206.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>亚明</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>⑥五老松　亚明</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入8号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1988\\01\\8811040207.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>周菱</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm